{"arkId":"cl010097019","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010097019","modified ":"2025-12-10","title":"Coffre des pierreries de Louis XIV","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Coffre des pierreries de Louis XIV"},{"type":"Ancien titre","value":"Coffre dit d\u0027Anne d\u0027Autriche"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1677","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1677,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"4e quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle = dernier quart du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Blanck, Jakob","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"MS 159","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"coffret","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Coffre en ch\u00eane recouvert de soie bleue pr\u00e9sentant cinq panneaux d\u0027or ajour\u00e9 et cisel\u00e9 pr\u00e9sentant un d\u00e9cor de grands rinceaux d\u0027acanthe parsem\u00e9s de roses, tulipes, zinnias, narcisses, oeillets et lys, enrichi de petits feuillages de vigne, de fleurettes, de vrilles et de tiges, le tout dispos\u00e9s sym\u00e9triquement. Quatre pieds en or massif en forme de pattes de lion reposant sur des petits galets ; deux poign\u00e9es lat\u00e9rales \u00e0 d\u00e9cor de feuillages.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; N\u00b0 \u0022298\u0022 grav\u00e9 sous l\u0027un des pieds","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"25,2","displayDimension":"25,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"47,5","displayDimension":"47,5 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"36,2","displayDimension":"36,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Technique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Le coffre est pay\u00e9 au printemps 1676 \u00e0 Suzanne Lejeune, veuve de Jean Pitan, orf\u00e8vre ordinaire du Roi et surtout n\u00e9gociant. Le coffre reste dans les collections royales ; \u00e0 la Restauration au palais des Tuileries, en 1816 dans la chambre \u00e0 coucher du roi Louis XVIII, en 1826 dans celle de Charles X ; sous la Monarchie de juillet dans le Salon de famille de Louis-Philippe aux Tuileries. Il entre en 1852 dans les collections du Mus\u00e9e des Souverains.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"ancienne collection royale\/de la Couronne","doubt":"","dates":[]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"ancienne collection royale\/de la Couronne"}],"place":[{"value":"Paris"}],"objectType":[{"value":"coffret"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Dion-Tenenbaum, Anne (dir.), Les diamants de la Couronne et joyaux des souverains fran\u00e7ais, Editions Faton, 2023","bibliographyDate":"2023","bibliographyDetail":"p. 68, 280, cat. 8","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Bimbenet-Privat, Mich\u00e8le ; Doux, Florian ; Gougeon, Catherine, Orf\u00e8vrerie de la Renaissance et des Temps Modernes XVIe, XVIIe et XVIIIe si\u00e8cles. La collection du Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, 3 vol., [Paris, mus\u0